2)  program to find most repeated character and freequency from the paragraph
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
par=input()
d={}
for i in par:
    if i not in d:
        d[i]=1 
    else:
        d[i]=d[i]+1 
m=list(d.values())
r=max(m)
for i in d:
    if d[i]==r:
        print('character =',i,'and','frequency =',d[i])
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Input:
this is aditya degree college
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
character = e and frequency = 5
***********************************************************************
